# **01  Executive summary**

| **The core finding:** No app in India — or globally — has built a product whose primary purpose is to help a household decide what to eat today, grounded in Indian food culture, household composition, and regional identity. The meal decision category is empty. Foofoo is not entering a crowded market; it is creating a new one at the intersection of three large, growing, and adjacent markets. |
| --- |

