| **Household meal plan (not individual)** | ✅ Core design principle | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |

| **Reading the matrix:** Foofoo is the only product with ✅ on all 12 capabilities. No other product has more than 4. The top 4 rows — proactive daily suggestion, Indian household awareness, regional identity, member add-ons — have no competitor with even a partial solution. This is the whitespace. The bottom 8 rows are where competitors have partial solutions — but always for a different problem (ordering, tracking, cooking) rather than the meal decision. |
